duties_responsibilities.duty: Reorganize data from Teamcenter instances hosted in the US, including non-Production and Production environments.
Ensure ITAR/UKML clearance for technical resources working directly with the data.
Perform data identification, cleansing, and model assessment.
Manage Teamcenter volume, perform ETL cycles, and environment rollback.
Generate reports and queries to validate data reorganization.

education_certification.credential: Bachelor’s degree in Information Technology or related field (Master's preferred)
